:"fdd973afcc4830b3a4d15b1f15272c49ab42e4dc","tid":659262,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-10T03:20:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>都係高189小小 當193 都唔算話好鬼高...</blockquote><br />\n190 其實都有，不過仲未知有邊個高過佢😄<br />\n<br />\n袁文傑 190cm 香港男演員與節目主持人。1991年畢業於無線電視藝員訓練班，1993年獲寶麗金卡拉OK模特兒大賽冠軍，現是亞洲電視合約男藝員，現今已是亞視力捧的當家小生&rdquo;。形象健康親切，具有模特兒經驗。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n車保羅被流傳於入行前為商業電台停車場看更（保安員），因樣貌怪趣被羅致入行，後獲其本人澄清沒有此事[5]。由於他身高6呎4吋（190cm）[6]，加上擁有瘦長面型及像卡通人物的外形，故經常演出惹笑、怪人或奸人等角色。"},{"pid":"99633f994ae46acdf7fa8362ee58ecd7926ced0d","tid":659262,"uid":44730,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-10T03:22:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/martinlamhy/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fmartinlamhy%2F&d=wapzj4paykHaBJyKCXJ%2FoTA5unq%2FSd9ZKvr75NUD1%2F0%3D&h=adba30c2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/martinlamhy/</a></blockquote><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/p/tz_ixlPRPP/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2Ftz_ixlPRPP%2F&d=wapzj4paykHaBJyKCXJ%2FoTA5unq%2FSd9ZKvr75NUD1%2F0%3D&h=44647f47\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2Ftz_ixlPRPP%2F&h=a127c1f8\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/p/tz_ixlPRPP/</a><br />\n條友仲高過佢😯</blockquote>孫陽成兩米緊係高過佢啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你唔講真係唔知佢乜水😅"},{"pid":"9f5132e619ea53a28dde59278cb2202e6c26e5cb","tid":659262,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-10T03:23:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>曾華倩正撚到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n以前係咪梁朝偉條女<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/14/105309_dc4d89861da876a3fb8154d45d96f0b1.png\" data-thumbnail